What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Major grammar. Not major conversation. Pretty much everything is graded based on written work, not conversation.
There is a lot of work for this class but you learn a lot and Terry is a great instructor.

The HW assignments are incredibly lengthy and don't count for very much of the grade. Therefore, I would recommend taking it CR/D if you really want to improve your grammar. Otherwise, it becomes a ton of busy work.
